00:42.897 --> 00:44.630
Layla?

00:44.632 --> 00:45.998
Junior.

00:46.000 --> 00:47.733
Hey.

00:47.735 --> 00:49.201
(chuckling): Hey.

00:49.203 --> 00:51.470
When did you get back into town?

00:51.472 --> 00:54.039
Uh, um... just a few months ago.

00:54.041 --> 00:55.241
I'm sorry. You're...
you're all right?

00:55.243 --> 00:57.109
Oh, no. No, no, no.
I'm so sorry about that.

00:57.111 --> 00:58.777
I... I wasn't looking
at my phone. I swear.

00:58.779 --> 01:01.113
It's just...
pregnancy brain.

01:01.115 --> 01:02.848
Wow. You're, uh...

01:02.850 --> 01:04.617
(laughing):
I know, right?

01:04.619 --> 01:05.918
Wow.

01:07.221 --> 01:08.587
Congratulations.

01:08.589 --> 01:09.755
Thanks, thanks.

01:09.757 --> 01:12.358
Um, ready to pop soon.
(chuckles)

01:12.360 --> 01:14.693
Yeah, I can see
that. Uh...

01:14.695 --> 01:17.263
So, do you know
what you're having?

01:17.265 --> 01:18.430
Yeah. Boy.

01:18.432 --> 01:19.932
Wow. Really?

01:19.934 --> 01:21.667
That's great.
Yeah.

01:21.669 --> 01:23.902
Tory and I are already nailing
everything down at the house.

01:23.904 --> 01:27.373
(chuckles) Yeah, that's
probably not a bad idea.

01:27.375 --> 01:30.342
Yeah. Um...

01:30.344 --> 01:33.112
I-I have an appointment
to get to, but I...

01:33.114 --> 01:35.080
I would love to catch up
sometime and hear about Iraq.

01:35.082 --> 01:37.049
People say you're a hero.

01:37.051 --> 01:38.350
Yeah, I don't know about that,

01:38.352 --> 01:40.552
but I-I would love
to catch up sometime.

01:40.554 --> 01:44.023
Okay. Uh, I still have
the same number.

01:46.000 --> 01:52.074
