contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:54.302 --> 01:57.236
(laughing): I'm sorry
I almost killed you.

01:57.238 --> 01:58.270
Oh, no, it's all right.

01:58.272 --> 02:00.205
I-I need to be more alert
next time.

02:01.075 --> 02:03.242
Well, it's good to see you.

02:03.244 --> 02:04.977
Yeah, you too.

02:06.314 --> 02:07.680
We'll get that coffee soon.

02:07.682 --> 02:08.913
Absolutely. Yeah.

02:08.916 --> 02:11.150
(chuckles)
(horn honks)

02:13.254 --> 02:15.521
Bye.
All right.

02:27.468 --> 02:29.735
♪ ♪

02:46.754 --> 02:49.822
♪ ♪

03:09.143 --> 03:10.342
Yo. Who are you?

03:10.344 --> 03:12.745
Hey, yo, it's okay.
She's my sister.

03:13.447 --> 03:14.847
Oh, how about an intro?

03:14.849 --> 03:16.115
How about not?

03:16.117 --> 03:17.249
Hey. Get up.

03:17.251 --> 03:18.450
Chill, sis.

03:18.452 --> 03:20.686
Get up now.
Ow!

03:22.256 --> 03:24.390
Ow. Get off me!

03:24.392 --> 03:26.992
- What the hell is wrong with you?
- We're getting out of here.

03:26.994 --> 03:29.094
Screw off, Tani.
Are you kidding me?

03:29.096 --> 03:30.729
You don't think I'll hit you?

03:30.731 --> 03:32.765
Vice is moving in
on this place any minute,

03:32.767 --> 03:34.133
so we have to go now.

03:34.135 --> 03:36.368
You want me to bounce?
How's that gonna look?

03:36.370 --> 03:37.469
You want to go back in there?

03:37.471 --> 03:39.071
You want to get swept up
in the raid?

03:39.073 --> 03:40.305
Do you understand
that once you're

03:40.307 --> 03:41.607
in the system I can't help you?

03:41.609 --> 03:42.908
(vehicles approaching)

03:45.112 --> 03:47.780
Let's go. Now.

03:47.782 --> 03:50.649
Get on the bike now!

